description:
We create pictures in our mind, which controls our thoughts that affects our emotions, which affects our actions and brings good and bad results in our life. This video course will help you change negative pictures into positive pictures and bring the desired results in your life. Enjoy the course.

What will you learn in this course?

    1) Change pictures in your mind and take control of your life

    2) How the pictures work In your mind

    3) Change negative pictures to positive pictures in your mind

    4) Guided process to change pictures in your mind.

    5) Summary of the course

Swish Technique- Bonus
title: Change Pictures In Your Mind And Change Your Life
